94
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:53,520
They don't act in single candles, 
but across a series of moves. 

95
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:57,920
Reading the flow helps track 
their actions and intentions. 

96
00:08:57,920 --> 00:09:01,840
Each candle connects to the 
next, creating a rhythm. 

97
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:06,880
Breaking this rhythm often signals 
important changes in market direction.
  

98
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:13,440
Volume doesn't just validate single 
candles - it validates entire moves. 

99
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:18,160
Rising prices should see rising 
volume in a healthy trend. 

100
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:25,200
When analyzing flow, consider the whole context.
A candle that looks bullish alone might actually  

101
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:29,520
