Chapter 4: Volume Candles as the Truth-Teller 

103
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:40,800
Volume candles act as market truth-tellers, 
exposing the real story behind every price move. 

104
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:47,280
The first rule to spot genuine moves is simple 
- the volume must match the price action. 

105
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:51,920
A strong price rise needs strong 
volume to prove it's real.
  

106
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:58,240
Take a wide up candle with small wicks.
The high volume shows many traders joined in,  

107
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:03,680
proving the move has real support.
This matches the basic rule of effort  

108
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:10,000
versus result, big price moves need 
big effort shown through volume.
  

109
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:17,360
The opposite situation warns you of fake moves.
Picture a price rising with thin volume. This  

110
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:21,600
