Look at a series of rising candles, 
with growing volume, but no wicks. 

116
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:55,920
This can only mean buying volume - 
sellers aren't fighting back at all. 

117
00:10:55,920 --> 00:11:01,120
Such clean moves with rising volume 
signal genuine buyer strength.
  

118
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:07,600
Wide spread candles need matching volume.
If a big price move happens on weak volume,  

119
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:14,400
that warns you of potential manipulation. 
Real moves need real participation.
  

120
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:19,120
Let's break down a typical false move.
You see price shooting up with a  

121
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:24,640
