True strength shows in  

124
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:41,360
the details. When price rises steadily with each 
candle wider than the last, volume also increase. 

125
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:48,400
This rising volume confirms more traders join 
with each push higher, validating the whole move. 

126
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:53,920
Look for volume that matches candle 
size. Big candles need big volume.  

127
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:59,600
Small candles match with small volume.
When these don't match, something's wrong.  

128
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:06,080
This simple check helps avoid false moves.
 
Also, don't trust wicks without checking  

129
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:12,080
