Also, track volume intensity changes over time. 

174
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:29,440
Rising volume with wider candles 
confirms increasing market interest. 

175
00:16:29,440 --> 00:16:34,400
Falling volume with narrowing 
candles shows dropping interest. 

176
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:39,600
These shifts often predict big moves.
 
Smart money leaves clues through  

177
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:44,160
volume intensity patterns.
