Wide spread, high volume candles show strong  

182
00:17:06,320 --> 00:17:11,680
agreement about price direction.
Narrow spread, low volume candles  

183
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:17,360
show uncertainty or disinterest.
These volume intensity principles will  

184
00:17:17,360 --> 00:17:20,960
